criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Triple Negative Breast Cancer;

          -  Stage II or III;

          -  Performance Status ECOG <2 or Karnofsky >50%;

          -  Hematologic (minimal values):

        Absolute neutrophil count > 1,500/mm3 Hemoglobin > 10.0 g/dl Platelet count > 100,000/mm3

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Stage I or IV;

          -  other malignancies.
